"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Some events have been canceled or will start later because parts of the country are dealing with extreme heat. More than 165 million people are facing dangerous heat and humidity, with temperatures expected to stay at 38C (100F) for several days.\",            \"english_title\": \"Extreme Heat Affects Events\",            \"translated_version\": \"Algunos eventos han sido cancelados o empezar\u00e1n m\u00e1s tarde porque partes del pa\u00eds tienen mucho calor. M\u00e1s de 165 millones de personas enfrentan calor y humedad peligrosos, con temperaturas que se esperan que queden en 38C (100F) por varios d\u00edas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Calor Extremo Afecta Eventos\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Serena Williams has withdrawn from her planned Wimbledon doubles appearance with her older sister Venus due to a knee injury.\",            \"english_title\": \"Serena Williams Withdraws from Wimbledon\",            \"translated_version\": \"Serena Williams no jugar\u00e1 en Wimbledon con su hermana mayor Venus porque tiene una lesi\u00f3n en la rodilla.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Serena Williams No Jugar\u00e1 en Wimbledon\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Pope paid tribute to migrants who lost their lives at sea at a cemetery on the Italian island of Lampedusa.\",            \"english_title\": \"Pope Honors Migrants\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Papa honr\u00f3 a los migrantes que perdieron sus vidas en el mar en un cementerio en la isla italiana de Lampedusa.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Papa Honra a Migrantes\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky says the target is important infrastructure that makes money for Russia's war.\",            \"english_title\": \"Zelensky on Infrastructure Target\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de Ucrania, Volodymyr Zelensky, dice que el objetivo es infraestructura importante que hace dinero para la guerra de Rusia.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Zelensky sobre Objetivo de Infraestructura\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"West Bengal's decision to replace eggs in some school meals has started a bigger discussion about nutrition and choice.\",            \"english_title\": \"West Bengal's School Meal Change\",            \"translated_version\": \"La decisi\u00f3n de Bengala Occidental de cambiar los huevos en algunas comidas escolares ha comenzado una discusi\u00f3n m\u00e1s grande sobre nutrici\u00f3n y elecci\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Cambio en Comidas Escolares de Bengala Occidental\"        }    ]}"